# This installs some important base tools needed for unlocking and what comes after

# Install adb, fastboot, and romdump
sudo apt-get install android-tools-fastboot

# Download a tool, romdump
## http://cloud.addictivetips.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/01/romdump_v72.zip
### put "install" in the "tools" folder of your Android SDK

# Web Support pages
## HTC https://www.unlockbase.com/unlock-phone/htc/
## Sony http://unlockbootloader.sonymobile.com/instructions
## ASUS (need to download a special tool, search Google to find yours: 'ASUS download unlock bootloader tool [device model]')
